About Us
Vision
Mission

We are a leading independent third-party inspection, training, ISO certification, incident investigation, and personnel certification company. Since our establishment in the United Arab Emirates in 1997. Our goal is to assist commercial and industrial clients with protecting their employees, operations, and assets. Our continuous commitment to fairness and independence sets us apart. Unlike other organizations, we have no links to insurance-related businesses, ensuring that there are no conflicts of interest. We prioritize our clients' safety and well-being, by providing excellence in all aspects of our services.

Our vision is to be the undisputed leader for creating a more secure and resilient world. We want to set the global standard for excellence in Third-Party Inspection, Training, ISO Certification, Incident Investigation, and Personnel Certification services. We believe in enabling businesses to achieve the highest levels of safety, sustainability, and operational excellence through solid commitment to innovation, integrity, and continuous improvement. Our goal is to be a trusted partner, driving positive change in the industries we serve and contributing to a better, more secure future for our customers and their communities."

Our mission is to protect individuals, assets, and the environment by providing high-quality inspection, training, ISO certification, incident investigation, and personnel certification services. We are dedicated to creating a culture of safety and excellence by utilizing cutting-edge solutions, continuous learning, and the highest ethical standards. Our commitment extends beyond compliance; we want to inspire businesses to manage risks proactively, improve operational resilience, and build a safety-first mindset. We want to be our clients' trusted partner on their journey to a more secure future by providing outstanding expertise and personalized service.

Company Values

Integrity

We adhere to the highest ethical standards and believe that our long-term success is dependent on maintaining the relationships that keep our company growing. We believe that open and honest communication is critical to the firm's long-term success.

Efficiency

We hold ourselves accountable to our clients for the timely completion of any project. We will work to identify and implement cost-cutting measures wherever possible.

Teamwork

We believe that an open culture characterized by mutual respect, idea sharing, and a commitment to common goals contributes to our firm's overall productivity.

Professionalism

We are committed to competence, dependability, and excellence in providing professional services. We believe that our projects reflect our company's identity.

Customer Service

We are committed to not only achieving, but exceeding, our clients' expectations.

Message

CEO

As CEO of Team Safety Consultants LLC, it is my pleasure to welcome you to our company’s website. Our journey began with a clear mission: to provide unparalleled safety consulting services across the UAE. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction has been the cornerstone of our success.

At TSC , we understand the critical importance of safety in every aspect of life and business. Our experienced team of professionals is dedicated to delivering comprehensive safety solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of each client. We take pride in our ability to offer a wide range of services, including risk assessments, safety audits, training programs, and emergency response planning.

Our head office in Dubai, along with our branches in Abu Dhabi and Sharjah, allows us to effectively serve clients across the region. We continually strive to stay ahead of industry standards and regulations, ensuring that our clients receive the most current and effective safety strategies available.

       Saleh Alnusairat - Founder & CEO
